@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.exp((v0 + 0.05 + v0 + 0.17)))
    v0 = (wp.sin(0.57) - ((v2 + 0.21 - v1 + 0.80) + wp.sin(v0 + 0.22)))
    v0 = wp.cos((0.63 + wp.abs(tmp + 0.66)))
    tmp = wp.exp((0.64 + v1))
    v0 = (0.02 - wp.cos(wp.sin(v0 + 0.01)))
    data[tid] = v0
